sequenceDiagram
  actor User
  participant FE as Donate Page
  participant CS as /api/payments/checkout-session
  participant RP as Razorpay
  participant WH as /api/payments/razorpay/webhook
  participant DB as Supabase
  participant INV as Invoice Service

  User->>FE: Submit donation details
  FE->>CS: POST checkout payload
  CS->>DB: Upsert donor + create pending donation
  CS->>RP: Create order
  RP-->>CS: order_id
  CS->>DB: Save order_id + ledger/audit
  CS-->>FE: checkout config
  User->>RP: Complete payment
  RP->>WH: Signed webhook event
  WH->>DB: Verify + update donation status + ledger
  WH->>INV: dispatchDonationInvoice(donationId)
  INV->>DB: Read donation
  INV-->>User: Email receipt (SMTP)
